      • createPropertyChange

        public PropertyChange createPropertyChange(String id,
                                           PropertyValue newValue,
                                           Collection<Grade> grades)
        Creates and returns a PropertyChange for modifying the Property with the specified String identifier.
        Parameters:
        id - A String containing the identifier of the Property to be modified.
        newValue - A new PropertyValue for the Property (generated using a PropertyValueFactory), or null to leave the value unchanged.
        grades - New Grades for the Property (generated using a GradeFactory), or null to leave the grades unchanged.
        Returns:
        See above.
